Package io.ib67.astralflow.item.factory

Interface ItemPrototypeFactory

All Known Implementing Classes:
ItemPrototype
@AvailableSince("0.1.0") public interface ItemPrototypeFactory
The definition of prototypes for items. Determines how does the item look like (getPrototype()) and its empty state (getStatePrototype())
